image_analysis.description: A photograph of a storage area, likely a basement or utility room. Two black three-drawer lateral filing cabinets are the central focus. The right cabinet has its top drawer pulled open. On top of the cabinets are various items including a FedEx Express box, rolled-up documents, a red plastic milk crate filled with papers, and other loose documents. To the left of the cabinets is a rack holding numerous hanging file folders. In the foreground, a large cardboard box is partially visible. The background shows white doors, a metal duct system, and a white support pillar on the right. Yellow sticky notes are attached to the front of several drawers.
